		        <span class="label editorpick">Editor's Pick</span>
			</div>
			<p class="abstract">Harvard’s role in an increasingly connected world includes deep ties to Latin America, where faculty and students are engaged in a range of research projects and initiatives, from climate research in Brazil to disaster relief work in Chile to protecting Maya art and architecture in Honduras. </p>

